snippet.title: The Atlas: Renaissance Voyager
snippet.description:
The Atlas: Renaissance Voyager

System: NEC PC Engine CD-ROM²

Year: 1994

Genre: Simulation \ Strategy


*sighs*  If I would have known that this game was released in English on other platforms I would have first played it in English and then in Japanese. 


Now it is too late and I don't care anymore... :P
